### HTML
* `GET /` `StaticPagesController#root`


EXAMPLE RESTFUL ROUTES FOR USER
| Route Name   | URL               | HTTP Verb  |    Description                            |
|--------------|:-----------------:| ----------:|-------------------------------------------|
| `index`      | /users            | GET        | display a list of all users               |
| `new`        | /users/new        | GET        | show form to make new users               |
| `create`     | /users            | POST       | add new user to database                  |
| `show`       | /users/:id        | GET        | show info about one user                  |
| `edit`       | /users/:id/edit   | GET        | show edit form of one user                |
| `update`     | /users/:id        | PUT        | update a particular user                  |
| `destroy`    | /users/:id        | DELETE     | delete a particular user                  |






### API Endpoints
#### `users`
* Custom Routes
  - `GET /api/users/current_user` - get current user's info
  - `GET /api/users/find/{username}` - finds a user by username

* Restful Routes
  - `POST /api/users` - sign up a new user
  - `PATCH /api/users/:user_id` - edit an existing user
  - `DELETE /api/users/:user_id` - delete an existing user

#### `session`
* `POST /api/session` - login user
* `DELETE /api/session` - logout user

#### `servers`
* `POST /api/servers` - create a server
* `DELETE /api/servers/:server_id` - destroy a server
* `GET` /api/servers` - gets all servers
* `GET` /api/servers/:server_id - gets a server by server_id

#### `channels`
* `POST /api/channels` - create a channel
* `DELETE /api/channels/:channel_id` - destroys a channel
* `PATCH /api/channels/:channel_id` - edits a channel (eg. `channel_name`)

#### `channel_messages`
* `POST /api/channel_messages` - posts a message on channel
* `GET /api/channel_messages` - gets all of a channel's messages

#### `direct_messages`
* `POST /api/direct_messages` - sends a message to another user
* `GET /api/direct_messages` - gets all of the messages between two users

